<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.1">
<l>vāṉō raḷavum mutumunnīr vaḷarnta kālam valiyuruviṉ</l>
<l>mīṉāy vantu viyantuyyak koṇṭa taṇṭā maraikkaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>āṉā vuruvi lāṉāya ṉavaṉai yammā viḷaivayaluḷ</l>
<l>kāṉār puṟavil kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The herder boy in an imperishable form,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one whose eyes are [like] fresh lotuses,</l>
<l>Who took a powerful form coming as a fish,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [all] were saved, being amazed,</l>
<l>At the time when the ancient three waters [of the sea]</l>
<l rend="indent">swelled as far as the celestials,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw him for myself in Kaṇṇapuram on forest-filled land</l>
<l rend="indent">among large and lovely fertile fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
